### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333/api
@contentType = application/json

### Get all permits (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/permits

### Get permits with custom pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/permits?page=1&limit=3

### Create new permit record
POST {{baseUrl}}/permits
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "date": "2024-01-20",
  "time": "14:00:00",
  "note": "Medical appointment",
  "attachment": "medical_certificate.pdf"
}

### Create permit without attachment
POST {{baseUrl}}/permits
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": 2,
  "date": "2024-01-21",
  "time": "10:30:00",
  "note": "Family emergency"
}

### Create permit with attachment
POST {{baseUrl}}/permits
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "date": "2024-01-22",
  "time": "13:00:00",
  "note": "Academic conference",
  "attachment": "conference_invitation.pdf"
}

### Get specific permit by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/permits/1

### Update permit record
PUT {{baseUrl}}/permits/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "note": "Updated: Medical appointment - specialist consultation",
  "attachment": "updated_medical_certificate.pdf"
}

### Partial update permit
PUT {{baseUrl}}/permits/2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "attachment": "emergency_documentation.pdf"
}

### Update permit time
PUT {{baseUrl}}/permits/3
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "time": "12:30:00",
  "note": "Conference time updated"
}

### Delete permit record
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/permits/1

### Try to get deleted permit (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/permits/1